{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place water in mixing bowl. Insert simmering basket and weigh in potatoes then steam <nobr>15 min\/Varoma\/speed 2.5<\/nobr>. Remove simmering basket with aid of spatula and discard water from mixing bowl.","Place onions, oil and fresh chilli in mixing bowl then chop <nobr>5 sec\/speed 5<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then sauté <nobr>5 min\/Varoma\/speed <\/nobr>.","Add beetroot, chilli powder, garam masala, salt and reserved steamed potatoes then mash <nobr>2 sec\/speed 5<\/nobr>. Transfer to a bowl and leave to cool completely in fridge.","Once mixture is cool, with wet hands, form 10 small, round patties (Ø 5 cm). Dust lightly with flour then place on a floured plate.","Heat a little oil in a frying pan over a medium heat. Fry patties in batches for 3-5 minutes on each side until browned. Drain on paper towel. Serve warm with pickles, chutneys or yoghurt."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["1000 g water","350 g potatoes, peeled, cut in pieces (2 cm)","70 g onions, quartered","15 g vegetable oil, plus extra for frying","1 fresh green chilli, halved, deseeded","100 g cooked beetroot, quartered","1 tsp Kashmiri chilli powder","1 tsp garam masala","1 tsp fine sea salt","1 Tbsp plain flour, for dusting"]}],"id":"r111493","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-eQcLOhlqZYw\/XZMvaX7dBZI\/AAAAAAAAaRg\/AFu2SX4ZQwsVIHWjPPBQyKbvthq455UlACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_fvVD9UwrirtXEDCM.png","title":"Aloo Beetroot Tikki","publishedAt":"2017-04-01T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"1.25 g","fat":"1.79 g","uom":"per 1 piece","carbohydrates":"8.69 g","calories":"234 kJ \/ 56 kcal"},"usefulItems":"paper towel, frying pan, refrigerator, hob","hintsAndTricks":["The beetroot provides a refreshing, healthier twist on these traditional little potato-based patties. They make a delicious light meal with salad and chutney, or as part of a larger Indian banquet.","For a smoother mixture, increase mashing time in step 3 to <strong>3 sec\/speed 5<\/strong>."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","1h","10 pieces"]}